{"tid":710861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏盡全球] 環時:中方不排除針對道指上市巨擘反擊","createTime":"2018-06-21T05:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T10:23:51.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"08046687c9d61e5774493f4bb018ffd52ca9eb44","tid":710861,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"內地《環球時報》英文版警告，倘若美國總統特朗普持續加劇與中國的貿易緊張關係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中方不排除會針對美國道瓊斯指數的上市巨擘來反擊</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》發表評論文章重申，中國不會偏離改革開放的道路，並且將進一步向全球開放市場，稱這可能會令資金由美國轉移至中國，繼而打擊美國公司的股價。"},{"pid":"c38426da80782c5ad3f58cbd7a1f55fef1f3e3cd","tid":710861,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:55:13.000Z","msg":"好撚驚呀"},{"pid":"c65c2183259b70523a7f632f077bc405afdfac9c","tid":710861,"uid":156005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/135552_2760735506a5bc187a35f6c829fae70d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F135552_2760735506a5bc187a35f6c829fae70d.jpg&h=9b9de5a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/135553_028241ab41eae95f755b662730cc7343.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F135553_028241ab41eae95f755b662730cc7343.png&h=a5990b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410fbebec6e4f3df9e9977df070268fc8dd79030","tid":710861,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"Chi-na: I bright sword, USA can eat banana la"},{"pid":"ac28f795f6e766e93000d9cec17c9bda72a40e4f","tid":710861,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:57:12.000Z","msg":"似乎想攪蘋果喎"},{"pid":"51b0abfd43380e2d9766addd8f75cf99f31